Program 1:
my.name = readline("Enter your name :")
age<-readline("Enter your age :")
age<-as.integer(age)
print(paste("Hi,",my.name,"next year you will be ",age+1,"years old"))
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Output:
> my.name = readline("Enter your name :")
Enter your name :NK
> age<-readline("Enter your age :")
Enter your age :18
> age<-as.integer(age)
> print(paste("Hi,",my.name,"next year you will be ",age+1,"years old"))
[1] "Hi, NK next year you will be  19 years old"
