Program 4:
x = 10.5
class(x)
x = 1000
x<-as.integer(x)
class(x)
x = 90i+98
class(x)
x = "Hi Nana"
class(x)
x = TRUE
class(x)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Output:
> x = 10.5
> class(x)
[1] "numeric"
> x = 1000
> x<-as.integer(x)
> class(x)
[1] "integer"
> x = 90i+98
> class(x)
[1] "complex"
> x = "Hi Nana"
> class(x)
[1] "character"
> x = TRUE
> class(x)
[1] "logical"
